ctures. A thorough analysis of computing timeand performance gain with\nseveral GPU parallel optimisation strategies show that it can leadto excellent\nperformance in hybrid computing environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Dec 2020 08:57:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-14"}
